{"tid":2336523,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國國會兩院通過的2021支出法案，當中(文件1471頁)提及資助香港民主運動，金額不少於三百萬美元","createTime":"2020-12-22T16:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T17:28:51.000Z","uid":378134,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0331721f2d91758419e6be3537060c193cdde93a","tid":2336523,"uid":378134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:02:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/UnitedHK18/5844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUnitedHK18%2F5844&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpCKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=4eb92e74\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/UnitedHK18/5844</a><br />\n美國國會兩院通過的2021支出法案，當中(文件1471頁)提及資助香港民主運動，金額不少於三百萬美元。<br />\nSEC.611及SEC.1107A(附件658頁）指示國家情報總監（與中央情報局、聯邦調查局、國家安全局、國防情報局、副國務卿等合作)每年需向國會提交香港國安系統的報告，直至2047年。<br />\n內容包括（一連串國家級起底）：香港國安及警務處國安公處人員名單、職位、國安公處架構及指揮、國安在多大程度上受中央控制; 亦包括香港國安系統與中國的合作機制; 國安及國安公處（國安系統）在前線的執法; 評估國安系統有否對個人進行拷問逼供; 評佔國安系統如何促使自我審查及貪污; 討論其戰術及doctrine，並包括如何使用高科技協助監控、偵察、控制，等新疆式數碼威權主義手段; 國安系統及其資金，以及有多少來自香港政府; 國安系統所用的監控技術來源自那間公司等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3sxGpuv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3sxGpuv.png&h=03ddad90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2f49ecf2f087f34a7863f44768f752ed2a3b3a8","tid":2336523,"uid":378134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581cde8d227004ba9ea77f48b5ae7055e05cc0f8","tid":2336523,"uid":378134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b37172aadf8cd1e8d8540292af1946c4cc90bb3","tid":2336523,"uid":378134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440a2e932565fd3165c3ebf36bb75b620f6c97ac","tid":2336523,"uid":378134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08cc6fef45766e9aaf755e369608da5dde755f5","tid":2336523,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T17:28:51.000Z","msg":"香港國安及警務處國安公處人員名單、職位、國安公處架構及指揮、國安在多大程度上受中央控制;<br />\n<br />\n原來一早已經有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}